Plastic containers for storing and organizing household and kitchen goods; bakeware; cookware, namely, pots, pans, skillets, strainers, colanders, and pot covers; dinnerware; beverage glassware; household utensils, namely, sieves, flour sifters, basting spoons, bread boards, carving boards, knife boards, pastry boards, wine bottle cradles, bottle openers, dishwashing brushes, floor brushes, scraping and scrubbing brushes, pot cleaning brushes,...
Containers for laundry and storage
Table linen, namely, coasters, napkins, runners, placemats, and tablecloths; kitchen towels; bath accessories, namely, bath towels and bath linens; bed linens; bedding, namely, shams, bed sheets, bed pads, mattress pads, bed blankets, and bed spreads; pillow cases and shams; plastic coasters; cloth coasters; comforters; curtains; duvets; oven mitts; textile napkins; quilts; shower curtains; slip covers; table cloths not of paper; table covers,...
Artificial plants; artificial fruit and flower arrangements; buttons for clothing; hair accessories, namely, twisters, snap clips, and bows; embroidery; embroidery equipment, namely, embroidery needles; artificial flowers; silk flower arrangements
