On Friday, August 30, 2002,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        B. SMITH WITH STYLE HOME COLLECTION by 
                        Smith, Barbara, New York 10036.
                        The USPTO has given the B. SMITH WITH STYLE HOME COLLECTION 
                        trademark serial  number of  78159754.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
